name: Hu Tao (Genshin Impact)
description:
LoRA

A LoRA for Hu Tao from Genshin Impact. This LoRA may also be able to yield results with Boo Tao.

All sample images are generated with my custom merged model UmbraMix

Prompts

  • Positive prompts should have a minimum of details about the character. Even if hu tao \(genshin impact\) is the main trigger word, when used by itself may produce unwanted results.

  • Negative prompts should be as simple as possible such as (worst quality, low quality:1.4), (blurry:1.4).

  • All sample prompts are generate with a CLIP SKIP value of 2

Weights

I recommend using the fallowing weights:

  • Closest to the character : 0.85 ~ 1.0

  • When trying to add / change the character clothing/assets : 0.5~0.75
